<h2 class="text-center">{l s='Display settings' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h2>
<hr>
{l s='Choose tab and configure it. You can chose only one tab' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Setting the display by Category' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '7.jpg'}
{l s='Check categories. Sticker will appear on products belonging to selected categories.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{l s='Field:' mod='seosaproductlabels'}
<strong>{l s='"Display in subcategories".' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong><br>
{l s='If you select' mod='seosaproductlabels'}
<strong>{l s='"Yes"' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong>
{l s=', the logo will be displayed for the categories you have selected.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{l s='If you select ' mod='seosaproductlabels'}
<strong>{l s='"No"' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong>
{l s=', stickers will be displayed only by default category.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{get_image_lang path = '8.jpg'}
<strong>{l s='Excluded products.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong>
{l s='You can exclude the display on individual products. To do this, enter the name of the product and select it.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<strong>{l s='Included products.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong>
{l s='If you select products in this field, then stickers will be displayed only for these products.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by manufacturer' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '9.jpg'}
{l s='Click on the field and select the required manufacturers. You can enter name to search for manufacturers.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by suppliers' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '10.jpg'}
{l s='Click on the field and select the required suppliers. You can enter name to search for suppliers.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by Status' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '11.jpg'}
{l s='Select the status of the item. A sticker will appear on products with selected status.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<strong>{l s='New' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong>
{l s='- is the status assigned to the product after its creation. The duration of this status is defined in the Prestashop settings.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<strong>{l s='Sale' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</strong>
{l s='- option customizable in products.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by  Cart rule' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '12.jpg'}
{l s='You can display stickers on products according to cart rules.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{l s='This option works only if specific products were specified in cart rules.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by Condition' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '13.jpg'}
{l s='Select necessaru variant' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by Bestsellers' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '14.jpg'}
{l s='Sticker will apply to best seller products.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
<h3 class="text-center">{l s='Display setting by Quantity' mod='seosaproductlabels'}</h3>
{get_image_lang path = '15.jpg'}
{l s='Stickers will be displayed on products, the number of which fits specified conditions.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{l s='Select position for label. This is position on image of product for label.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{get_image_lang path = '16.jpg'}
{l s='Mark user groups.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{l s='The sticker will be displayed only for users belonging to the selected groups.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{get_image_lang path = '17.jpg'}
{l s='You can limit the display of stickers on the price of the product. The sticker will be displayed only on those products that are included in the conditions of a given price. If the price fields are left blank, the price check will not be' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{l s='You can limit the display of stickers by date. the sticker will be displayed only in the specified period. If the fields with the date are left blank, the check by date will not be' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>
{get_image_lang path = '18.jpg'}
{l s='After all settings, save your changes.' mod='seosaproductlabels'}<br>